{
  "stem": "17.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 242.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say, when you have a better apartment, better house, in a better section, that was immediately evacuated for the German officials.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then you went down the line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And eventually, we all ended up in the ghetto which was already [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in 1940.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was more or less established, the borders of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was, of course, the oldest and the poorest part of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the Polish occupants, they were offered other quarters in other parts of the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the Jewish population was supposed to get ahold of some living quarters within the borders of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now let me go back before the ghetto, because that was important time for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My husband was following me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My husband was following me to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He escaped with his father, trying to save him [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the east part of Poland where they were from.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he still decided to look for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came to Warsaw and we decided to get married at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But one incident if, I might say, private, the personal, so as long as we still lived in our original homes, the German soldiers and all their supporters, either if they were Ukrainians or some other collaborators were permitted to come to the house to plunder, to rape.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had full power over us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this group of younger, German, inexperienced soldiers came to the house, and they ask for jewelry or some other valuables.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We said that we already delivered accordingly to these [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] laws and decrees, but they still wanted this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wanted me and another person in this house to undress so they could examine the clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
